# Blog Content Directory

This directory will contain all blog posts in MDX format.

Each post should have frontmatter matching this schema:

```yaml
---
title: Post Title
description: Post description for SEO
pubDate: 2025-10-14
tags: [tag1, tag2]
image:
  url: /path/to/image.png
  alt: Image alt text
readingTime: 10 min
featured: false
---
```
